<bibRefCitation id="AA674B39FFB57458FE34FEE2FD09FE9B" author="Sclater, P. L. &amp; Salvin, O." box="[420,699,333,359]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="486 - 550" refId="ref23860" refString="Sclater, P. L. &amp; Salvin, O. (1879) On the birds collected by the late Mr. T. K. Salmon in the state of Antioquia, United States of Colombia. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London, 1879, 486 - 550. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1879. tb 02684. x" type="journal article" year="1879">Sclater &amp; Salvin, 1879</bibRefCitation>
